      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've heard from friends that a tiny bit of alcohol can actually make the meds work more effectively for relaxation. like, if i just have one small glass, won't the effect just be slightly stronger? it doesn't seem like it would be a big deal if it's just a sip or two to help me relax.",
