    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just really struggling with the insomnia though and it's making me so anxious. if i take the diazepam and just have one single glass of wine, like a normal amount for a person my size, is there really a chance it would actually be life threatening? it feels like such an extreme reaction for just a little bit of wine. wouldn't my body just process it normally?",
